1.Text summarization (Claude vs Jasper AI)
Claude gives more accurate and well-structured summaries, while Jasper AI produces simpler and more readable summaries.

2. Code generation (Microsoft Copilot vs Meta LLaMA)
Microsoft Copilot generates more practical and executable code, whereas Meta LLaMA may require more corrections.

3. Creative writing (Jasper AI vs Claude)
Jasper AI is more creative and expressive, while Claude is more coherent and logically organized.
